<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176365>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Anoplodelphys laubieri n. sp. holotype female (MNHN-Cp 2315). A, Cephalosome and first pedigerous somite, lateral; B, urosome, lateral. Anoplodelphys incerta Lafargue & Laubier, 1977, holotype female (ZMA CO. 106.602). C, Cephalosome and first pedigerous somite, ventral, D, Antennule showing surface ornamentation; E, Leg 5. Scale bars: A = 500 μm, B = 50 μm, C – D = 200 μm, E = 25 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176365/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

